{"tid":1037373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請勿在車廂內打飛機","createTime":"2019-02-26T01:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T01:57:43.000Z","uid":146434,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c05e26d91316663c8590aa67cd60cdaf8daf9f1e","tid":1037373,"uid":146434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:43:21.000Z","msg":"朝早搭西鐵 有個阿叔打飛機<br />\n但佢前面既人都碌緊ig 或者坐低訓教<br />\n偏偏好似得我望到佢做緊乜<br />\n我仲以為自己睇錯 點知佢望住我笑<br />\n我就即刻拎電話出黎想影低佢<br />\n但佢就停晒手 背對住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪要好似港鐵咁講聯絡車長先有用<br />\n定係要當場大叫「喂你做緊咩」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉成車好似得我睇到 而我又冇做到野阻撓到個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得自己好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830b50cd1f8ef2d896857f58b5740dd2e7372ecb","tid":1037373,"uid":166827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:47:03.000Z","msg":"相呢？又話影低左"},{"pid":"a564afe4ebd614875d479d9b16563db10437c623","tid":1037373,"uid":68607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"衝過去幫佢含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977b8277a3ab2d501fbd621314c1bc143abaf782","tid":1037373,"uid":146434,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"830b50cd1f8ef2d896857f58b5740dd2e7372ecb","tid":1037373,"uid":166827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1